{"timestamp": "2026-02-28T16:38:03.732808+00:00", "source": "camelfinance.co.uk/lessons/gold-macroeconomic-cycles-and-seasonal-patterns-in-the-yellow-metal", "topic": "Camel Finance: Understanding Macro and Seasonal Cycles - Gold: Macroeconomic Cycles and Seasonal Patterns in the Yellow Metal", "findings": "Key Macro & Seasonal Drivers: Gold has long been a barometer of macroeconomic conditions. Its price cycles are heavily influenced by factors like inflation, interest rates, and global risk sentiment, as well as well-defined seasonal demand patterns:

